title: i played a game and got s- and havent recived a chest
body:
I played a game as janna and got s- and also own the champion but didn't recive a chest
this is would be my first chest of the month aswell so I cant see why I haven't recived one ???

replies.body: Hmmmmm yea that's kinda of odd tbh. It looks like that match hasn't been fully uploaded to our servers yet on the backend, so it may take a little while for that chest to pop up. If it still hasn't shown up in a few hours, hit me back up and I can see what I can do.
